HEADWORD: Brochure
<hw>Bro*chure"</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F., fr.
<ets>brocher</ets> to stitch. See <er>Broach</er>, <pos>v.
t.</pos>]</ety> <def>A printed and stitched book containing only a few
leaves; a pamphlet; a single sheet folded to make four pages.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

